SYNOPSIS

    In dist.ini:

     [PerlStripper]

DESCRIPTION

    This module lets you strip your modules/scripts with Perl::Stripper
    during build.

CONFIGURATION

 maintain_linum => bool

 strip_ws => bool

 strip_comment => bool

 strip_pod => bool

 strip_log => bool

 stripped_log_levels => str

    Comma-separated string.

SEE ALSO

    Dist::Zilla

    Perl::Stripper

